{"word":"καλύβη","slug":"καλύβη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καλύβη</b></el> <el>(κᾰλύ˘βη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:καλύπτω'><el>καλύπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a hut, cabin, cell</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>tugurium</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a cover, screen</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}